Masyado akong naging pabaya.

00:13:00.320 --> 00:13:02.400
May tumawag sa akin
para i-inspect ang bago mong gown.

00:13:03.240 --> 00:13:04.720
Kung hindi namagitan si Miss Jiuning,

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:06.120
pinatay ka na sana.

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:08.520
Salamat, Miss Jiuning.

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:10.480
Huwag mong banggitin, Surong.

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:12.800
Noong ako ay nasa gulo,

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:15.960
Consort Shu at tinulungan mo ako.

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.920
Naparito ako upang ipakita ang aking pasasalamat ngayon

00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:19.920
at nangyari

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:21.720
para tumakbo sa kontrabida.

00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:23.760
Ito ay aming tungkulin

00:13:23.960 --> 00:13:25.320
para protektahan ang ating mga amo.

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:26.480
Jiuning.

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:28.200
tinulungan kita

00:13:28.680 --> 00:13:29.960
dahil sa habag

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:31.640
para sayo.

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.240
Wala kang utang sa akin.

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.760
Tinatrato ng iyong Kamahalan ang lahat

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:37.520
mabait.

00:13:37.960 --> 00:13:39.840
Paano mo nasaktan ang sinuman?

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:41.640
wala akong hinahanap

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:43.920
higit pa sa pag-iingat sa sarili.

00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:47.080
Marahil ay masyado akong malapit kay Consort Chun.

00:13:47.880 --> 00:13:49.200
Ngayong nahulog na siya,

00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:50.960
magiging ako

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:52.960
ibinaba sa kanya.

00:13:53.760 --> 00:13:54.400
Kamahalan.

00:13:54.960 --> 00:13:56.320
Kahit kulang ka sa lakas

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:57.080
mga koneksyon,

00:13:57.560 --> 00:13:59.520
hawak mo na ngayon ang marangal na ranggo ng Consort.

00:14:00.080 --> 00:14:01.840
How dare they disregard the law?

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:02.880
Hindi nila kaya

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:04.000
i-bully lang kita.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:04.560
Surong.

00:14:05.240 --> 00:14:05.920
Isipin ang iyong mga salita.

00:14:10.280 --> 00:14:11.840
(Parang si Consort Shu)

00:14:12.640 --> 00:14:13.960
(Siya ay nagpapahiwatig ng isang bagay.)

00:14:15.640 --> 00:14:18.480
(Anong klaseng tao siya?)

00:14:19.120 --> 00:14:20.760
(Bakit si Xiao Zhuozi?)

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:22.880
(subukang patayin si Consort Shu?)

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.000
(Relate ba ito kay Noble Consort Xian?)

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:30.720
Kamahalan, mag-iingat ka.

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:32.360
Maiwan na kita para magpahinga.

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:34.040
I take my leave.

00:14:46.784 --> 00:14:47.360
Xiaotao.

00:14:49.480 --> 00:14:50.160
Miss Jiuning.

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:51.920
Sabi ng Kataastaasan

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:53.680
maulan ngayon.

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.360
Sikat na ang araw ngayon.

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:58.400
Ilipat natin ang mga bulaklak
sa labas para sa araw

00:14:58.560 --> 00:14:59.160
at putulin ang mga ito

00:14:59.520 --> 00:15:00.160
medyo.

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:01.360
Nandito na kami.

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:06.360
wala doon

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:09.240
ilang kaldero ng
paboritong balsamo ng Kataas-taasan?

00:15:09.680 --> 00:15:10.440
Nasaan ang mga iyon?

00:15:11.200 --> 00:15:11.880
Kalimutan mo na.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.560
Yung mga balsamo

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:14.800
lahat namatay.

00:15:15.640 --> 00:15:16.440
Namatay sila?

00:15:16.600 --> 00:15:17.120
Oo.

00:15:17.312 --> 00:15:17.880
Bakit?

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:20.360
Sila ay namamayagpag noon.

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.120
Paano sila namatay?

00:15:24.360 --> 00:15:26.000
Si Xiao Zhuozi ay naging pabaya

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:27.280
sa trabaho sa mga araw na ito.

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:28.440
kahit papaano,

00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:30.840
pinatay niya ang lahat ng balsamo na iyon.

00:15:31.400 --> 00:15:32.640
At sinasadya niya

00:15:32.920 --> 00:15:35.520
nabasag ang plorera
na iniregalo ng Kanyang Kamahalan sa Kanyang Kamahalan.

00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:36.720
Galit na galit siya

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:37.640
at pinarusahan siya.

00:15:39.120 --> 00:15:40.080
sinasadya?

00:15:41.200 --> 00:15:42.600
Mga araw bago ang kanyang kamatayan,

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:46.360
naging pabaya siya
sa mga utos ng Kamahalan,

00:15:46.920 --> 00:15:48.320
pag-iwas sa mga responsibilidad

00:15:48.560 --> 00:15:49.280
buong araw.

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:51.040
Xiaotao. Gabi na.

00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:52.200
Bilisan mo.

00:15:52.832 --> 00:15:53.376
Sige.

00:15:58.520 --> 00:15:59.160
Xiao Luzi.

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:00.280
may tanong ako.

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:01.680
- Xiao Zhuozi...
- Pakiusap.

00:16:01.840 --> 00:16:02.440
Miss Jiuning.

00:16:03.080 --> 00:16:03.640
Xiao Zhuozi...

00:16:05.160 --> 00:16:06.640
Si Xiao Zhuozi ay nasa problema.

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:08.800
Bawal namin siyang pag-usapan.

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:11.480
Xiao Luzi.

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:14.480
Nagtrabaho ka kay Xiao Zhuozi nang maraming taon.

00:16:15.400 --> 00:16:16.840
Hindi mo ba naisip ang kanyang kamatayan

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:18.720
ay kahina-hinala?

00:16:20.960 --> 00:16:22.200
Parang kakaiba.

00:16:22.640 --> 00:16:24.280
Ilang gabi na ang nakalipas,

00:16:24.640 --> 00:16:27.160
Nakita ko siyang palihim na nagpupunas ng luha

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:28.400
habang nagbubulungan

00:16:28.920 --> 00:16:29.680
mga bagay tulad ng,

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:31.480
"Walang daan palabas".

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.400
(Pwede ba)

00:16:35.280 --> 00:16:37.080
(na pinilit ng Her Highness si Xiao Zhuozi)

00:16:37.520 --> 00:16:38.760
(para patayin si Consort Shu?)

